                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Badinguet est un gueux, mais Badinguet l'emporte ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "C'est lui qui tient le sac en ses doigts triomphants,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Il est temps de songer à mes petits enfants.",
